data.description: Pictures don't do this one justice!  The green rolling hills and century oaks make the sunset and sunrise perfect everyday.  The fully remodeled and updated home on a hill has endless private views.  Enter through the front to the large vaulted ceiling with wooden beams, spacious dining room and bright kitchen with butcher block counters. Continue down the hall to the large secondary bedrooms and spacious master retreat. Exit out the enclosed patio to the large sparkling pool next to the majestic oak. The new livestock barn and corral has an equipment shed and livestock weather shelters.  New improvements to the property include a shipping container, new fence and working pens for livestock, metal roof, rain gutters and well house.  With only a 3 minute drive to I-10 this property is in the perfect location to get where you need to go and enjoy quiet and private hill country sunsets everyday.
